{"tid":1874302,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［社區爆發］根本係呢一刻唔應該再有街頭示威，你地仲嘈乜？","createTime":"2020-02-11T06:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T07:44:47.000Z","uid":219007,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b63e9357844559a854ec0048e4d2ca3d9e393b43","tid":1874302,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:37:27.000Z","msg":"你哋喺度討論預約開花、突發開花、匿名搞手同遊行集會邊樣好，其實你哋有冇諗過呢一刻社區已經爆發，係幾個月之內香港將會變成死城，到時再有街頭行動擾亂社會秩序已經增加唔到任何社會代價，因為本身已經係死城，咁做仲會增加示威者之間感染機會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n777依家係要攬炒就應該成全佢<br />\n現時嘅目標就係係拖垮經濟下而又保住自己條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到瘟疫完結先在準備下一波街頭鬥爭<br />\n明母？"},{"pid":"7caedafcb1dbf64cb1ef2f32f8f98b96af92ad91","tid":1874302,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:37:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">喺屋企家居隔離緊？<br />\n無口罩出唔到街？<br />\n咁快啲過嚟<span style=\"color: blue;\">Twitter</span>戰線！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要光復香港撳幾個掣都唔得？</span></span><br />\nTwitterHelpBot嘅tasklist 24小時更新<br />\n入去 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=a3446825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">RT + Like + Comment</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. Rick Scott <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1226912446767562759?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1226912446767562759%3Fs%3D09&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=cd9e1b23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitte